  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 : 21\u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Extension of holiday for schools: Schools will be opened on 21st",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education has decided to grant three more days of holiday to all government and government-recognised private schools in the country.",
        "Accordingly, it has been decided to give a holiday to schools from next Monday (18) to Wednesday (20).",
        "It is noteworthy that the second term for this year will start on the 21st of July."
      ],
